name: Cubanacan - Mederos Habano - Fifty 3
additionalNotes: Mederos Habano Cigars are a medium to full-bodied smokes with a history dating back to nineteenth Century Cuba. Carefully assembled in Esteli, Nicaragua, Mederos stogies are encased in prime Corojo wrappers from Jalapa with covers and fillers from Esteli. Experience premium Nicaraguan tobacco combined with Cuban tradition.
